These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
City: new-york, berlin, nizza, boston
Pet: turtle, lizard, rat, hedgehog
1. City:berlin is between City:new-york and Pet:lizard##2
2. City:berlin is on the left or right of Pet:turtle##3
3. City:berlin is somewhere between City:boston and City:new-york##7
4. Pet:lizard is in an even position##4
5. City:boston is on the right of Pet:rat##1
6. Pet:lizard is somewhere to the left of Pet:turtle##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| City   | nizza | boston       | berlin | new-york        |
| Pet      | rat  | lizard | hedgehog        | turtle |

