2. Food:avocado is somewhere to the left of Food:pumpkin##5
3. Food:avocado is somewhere to the right of House:townhouse##5
4. Food:asparagus is on the left of Food:avocado##1
5. House:townhouse is between House:modern and House:palace##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Food     | mango | asparagus       | avocado         | pumpkin     |
| House   | palace   | townhouse | modern | cottage |

