.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
Transport: scooter, skateboard, airplane, ship
Cigar: alhambra, old-henry, swisher, fonseca
1. Cigar:fonseca is on the far left or far right##3
2. Transport:scooter is somewhere between Cigar:old-henry and Transport:ship##7
3. Transport:airplane == Cigar:fonseca##1
4. Cigar:swisher is on the left of Cigar:fonseca##1
5. Transport:skateboard is on the left of Cigar:alhambra##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Transport   | skateboard | scooter | ship       | airplane |
| Cigar   | old-henry      | alhambra   | swisher | fonseca  |

