2. Pet:hamster is somewhere to the left of Pet:goat##5
3. Beverage:almond-milk is on the right of Beverage:soy-milk##1
4. Pet:turtle is somewhere between Beverage:iced-tea and Beverage:almond-milk##7
5. Pet:turtle is on the left of Pet:fish##1
6. Pet:goat is somewhere to the left of Pet:turtle##5
7. Beverage:iced-tea is on the far left or far right##3
8. Beverage:almond-milk is on the left or right of Beverage:soy-milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
